{"tid":762115,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(好波)  一帶一路夥伴　傳巴基斯坦獲中國貸20億美元","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:40:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54780726d8988e33c58c23090adaae96b68d776b","tid":762115,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，早前市傳「一帶一路」夥伴國之一的巴基斯坦正尋求向國際貨幣基金組織(IMF)借貸最多120億美元，目前則有報道指出，中國願意向該國貸款20億美元，令貨幣盧比急彈3%，收報124盧比兌每美元，創2008年10月以來最大升幅。該國的高級官員亦否認接觸IMF。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指出，近日有數據顯示，巴基斯坦國家銀行的外匯儲備只剩下90億美元，很快就「乾塘」，必須尋求援助。一旦該國向IMF求援，由於貸款將會受到規管，恐令投資總額逾600億美元的中巴(中國、巴基斯坦)經濟走廊受阻。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，巴基斯坦一直用「走廊建設可能受阻」為由，要求中國借款，以避免向IMF求援。今年上半年中國已借出合共40億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180730/bkn-20180730221125172-0730_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180730%2Fbkn-20180730221125172-0730_00842_001.html&d=IuKNOLbpE%2FhetUGzojZuLbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=e091932e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180730/bkn-20180730221125172-0730_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"169f5522b4edc935c7978431b60f983e95243ae9","tid":762115,"uid":1556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a731885e329614ca97085e9ccb43e45edcf5cb3f","tid":762115,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a523430d20d851ba52e7a841d40052f699fd83db","tid":762115,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"巴基躝坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b647d0fe1c9bd0918ff2be47d5